ifferent screen sizes, ensuring a smooth shopping experience on smartphones and tablets.</span></span></h3></div></div><div class="_b7aca0c"><div class="_89d52dd mask" id="el-c90c939f-fd36-46ac-99a6-046b0c4b4953"><div data-leaf-element="true" class="_13b31d1"><amp-img layout="fill" src="https://www.hiddenbrains.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/11878914_Big_phone_with_cart.jpg" alt="11878914_Big_phone_with_cart" srcset="https://www.hiddenbrains.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/11878914_Big_phone_with_cart.jpg 5000w, https://www.hiddenbrains.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/11878914_Big_phone_with_cart-2048x2048.jpg 2048w, https://www.hiddenbrains.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/11878914_Big_phone_with_cart-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://www.hiddenbrains.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/11878914_Big_phone_with_cart-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://www.hiddenbrains.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/11878914_Big_phone_with_cart-768x768.jpg 768w, https://www.hiddenbrains.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/11878914_Big_phone_with_cart-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.hiddenbrains.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/11878914_Big_phone_with_cart-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.hiddenbrains.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/11878914_Big_phone_with_cart-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 47vh, 105vw" disable-inline-width="true" class="i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></div></div></div></div></div></amp-story-grid-layer></amp-story-page><amp-story-page id="9156a318-af0a-410e-9c46-8fb854a186b1" auto-advance-after="7s" class="i-amphtml-layout-container" i-amphtml-layout="container"><amp-story-grid-layer template="vertical" aspect-ratio="412:618" class="grid-layer i-amphtml-layout-container" i-amphtml-layout="container" style="--aspect-ratio:412/618;"><div class="_c84718f page-fullbleed-area"><div class="page-safe-area"><div class="_6120891"><div class="_89d52dd mask" id="el-4d95e4c2-6aae-475f-8b00-5462dde4115